OL,3,C'1 in 15,000': Baby born with rare
OL,4,Ccondition thriving due to life-saving
OL,5,Cscan
OL,7,FJessica Young was just 36 weeks
OL,8,Fpregnant when her son Sunny was
OL,9,Fdelivered by emergency caesarean
OL,10,Fsection at the John Radcliffe Hospital.
OL,12,FA routine scan had revealed that she
OL,13,Fhad placental insufficiency and Sunny
OL,14,Fwasn't getting enough oxygen or
OL,15,Fnutrients. What followed was a two
OL,16,Fmonth ordeal to save his life.
OL,18,FShortly after he was born, Sunny was
OL,19,Fdiagnosed with Beckwith-Wiedemann
OL,20,Fsyndrome.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
