FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777986670
OL,3,C'1 in 15,000': Baby born with rare
OL,4,Ccondition thriving due to life-saving
OL,5,Cscan
OL,7,FThe genetic condition, which affects
OL,8,Fone in 15,000 babies, causes parts of
OL,9,Fthe body to grow too much, including
OL,10,Fthe tongue and one side of the body.
OL,12,FIt also increases the risk of
OL,13,Fchildhood cancers.
OL,15,FSunny spent 62 days in hospital while
OL,16,Fhe received care. His mother, Jessica,
OL,17,Fsays it was the experiences of others
OL,18,Fwhich helped make everything more
OL,19,Fmanageable.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777986670
OL,3,C'1 in 15,000': Baby born with rare
OL,4,Ccondition thriving due to life-saving
OL,5,Cscan
OL,7,F"When Sunny was first born, one of the
OL,8,Ffirst things that I did was look
OL,9,Fonline for other people who have been
OL,10,Fthrough this, and it made it feel a
OL,11,Flot less scary," she said.
OL,13,F"I found somebody on Instagram who had
OL,14,Fposted lots of videos and photos of
OL,15,Ftheir son's experience and it just
OL,16,Fmade it feel so much more manageable."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777986670
OL,3,C'1 in 15,000': Baby born with rare
OL,4,Ccondition thriving due to life-saving
OL,5,Cscan
OL,7,FTen months later and Jessica and her
OL,8,Fhusband, Jake, say Sunny is now
OL,9,Fthriving although he'll have to have
OL,10,Fregular check-ups until around the age
OL,11,Fof seven.
OL,13,FAlthough there's no cure for the
OL,14,Fdisease, most children grow up to be
OL,15,Fhealthy adults so the Young's are
OL,16,Ffocusing on a positive future together.
OL,18,FJessica and Jake are walking 62km
OL,19,Facross the South West Coast Path to
OL,20,Frepresent the first 62 days of Sunny's
OL,21,Flife spent in hospital.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777986670
OL,3,C'1 in 15,000': Baby born with rare
OL,4,Ccondition thriving due to life-saving
OL,5,Cscan
OL,7,FAs well as raising money for charity,
OL,8,Fthe couple are set on raising
OL,9,Fawareness of Beckwith-Wiedemann
OL,10,Fsyndrome more widely.
OL,12,FThey also want to thank staff at
OL,13,FOxford's John Radcliffe Hospital for
OL,14,Fthe life-saving action they took after
OL,15,FJessica's pregnancy scan and the SSNAP
OL,16,Fcharity, which supports newborns and
OL,17,Ftheir parents.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
