CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777986670
OL,3,C'1 in 15,000': Baby born with rare
OL,4,Ccondition thriving due to life-saving
OL,5,Cscan
OL,7,FJake said: "Because it's so uncommon,
OL,8,Fand when you hear it's a syndrome, you
OL,9,Ffeel like this could be really bad.
OL,10,FYou're not really too sure.
OL,12,F"So to get more awareness out to
OL,13,Fpeople, you know, that there's a lot
OL,14,Fof support there, it's quite
OL,15,Freassuring to think, well, you know,
OL,16,Fthis is going to be okay."
OL,18,FWhat causes Beckwith-Wiedemann
OL,19,Fsyndrome (BWS)?
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
