OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1777986670
OL,3,C'1 in 15,000': Baby born with rare
OL,4,Ccondition thriving due to life-saving
OL,5,Cscan
OL,7,FBWS is caused by abnormalities at
OL,8,Fchromosome 11p15. There are a number
OL,9,Fof different abnormalities that we see.
OL,11,FThe names are quite complicated, but
OL,12,Fare important to the doctors so they
OL,13,Fcan give you the right advice.
OL,15,FMost of these cannot be inherited and
OL,16,Fhave a very low chance of happening
OL,17,Fagain in the family. These include:
OL,19,FWhat are the signs and symptoms of BWS?
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
